blog.name: west-coast-taylor
blog.title: 🌻 Always Stay Humble & Kind 🌻
blog.description:
" Someday you'll be just a memory

so make it count" . Hello ! My name is Lisa Cherie Curtis , and this is my blog . Im from Ventura County California . Kids Art Teacher 👩‍🏫🎨

Twitter : cherie_curtis13

My talented friend Followed 12/22/2014.

Born on a December 3rd in 1989. I blog about Tay , music and art . I also am an artist and do portraits of people , and animals, I wish I could afford to go to school, but since I cant I use my talent for good , and donate to help people and animals . Im also a distant relative of Taylors great great great grandfather on Taylors dads side . So does that even count? lol . I have a kitty named catastrophe . I make creative Lyric art and Taylor related things way more than I could ever count. I wore a snake dress and Merch for Reputation to the Grammy’s because I felt like it deserved to be recognized more . May 15th Taylor Surprised me in Vegas and it was beyond amazing and so incredibly sweet of her. I was just super super sick just gotten out of the e.r a day prior . but I never wanted to say or post about it , for people to think I was lying to meet her again. Because that’s not that case. I just want to feel fully there cause I never got to be myself that day. So I really wish one day for a make up day :) . But of course Im super great full ! I love christmas and get overly excited on holidays. I love vintage shopping and black and white things. So obviously I love Reputation. Just be kind to people. You never know what they are going through and just little things you do could make their day. I love the beach, and just sometimes laying on the grass gazing up at the stars and appreciating them , because I mean they are so remarkable if you think about it . And the beach breeze blowing in your hair , 80's music , Shania Twain, The Beach Boys , The eagles . I Love Lucy . Favorite movie is pretty in pink , and A Star is Born .
